summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 4.7°C) and outside temperature (up 3.6°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 8%) and rainfall (up 0.4 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 590 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 995 m) and light levels (up 5766 lux) when compared to today.
